title: ITIL V3 2011 eBooks with OCR
description:
I've looked and looked for these eBooks with clickable links and searchable text and haven't found them. Finally I found them (through a google search) on some obscure Russian FTP (The books are in English).

At first they had corrupted fonts, but I rebuilt them in Nitro PDF and they work perfectly!

These aren't scans of books, they contain searchable and selectable text.

Enjoy!

01 - ITIL V3 2011 Service Strategy.pdf - 21,820 KB
02 - ITIL V3 2011 Service Design.pdf - 15,209 KB
03 - ITIL V3 2011 Service Transition.pdf - 14,783 KB
04 - ITIL V3 2011 Service Operation.pdf - 14,942 KB
05 - ITIL V3 2011 Continual Service Improvement.pdf - 6,759 KB
